data.title: Is Cher engaged to Alexander Edwards? Here’s what the pop star shared
data.meta_description: Cher, the 76-year-old pop star, is in a romantic relationship with the 36 years old music executive Alexander Edwards. The rumours of engagement fueled as she shared the picture of a diamond ring.
data.text:
Synopsis

Cher, the 76-year-old pop star, is in a romantic relationship with the 36 years old music executive Alexander Edwards. The rumours of engagement fueled as she shared the picture of a diamond ring.

Music legend, Cher has fuelled the speculations of her engagement after she shared a picture of a diamond ring on her Twitter. The 76-year-old musician is said to be in a romantic relationship with music executive Alexander Edwards who is 36.

Cher confirmed their relationship in November this year by sharing a picture of her accompanying Alexander Edwards.

Fans believe the picture of the ring suggests that the couple might be taking their relationship a step further. Cher shared the picture of the glittering diamond ring on her Twitter account with the caption ‘THERE R NO WORDS, ALEXANDER, A.E..’

Thousands of congratulations flooded her post. Many fans speculated whether this is the news of her engagement or if it means something else while others are even sceptical of the relationship of the couple.

Cher has been a music legend. The news of her life frequently makes the headlines. She has been married two times in the past. Her first marriage was with Sonny Bono, with whom she shares her 53 years old son Chad. The couple separated in 1974. Soon after, Cher married Gregg Allman, and the couple shared a child Elijah Blue. Cher was married to Gregg Allman from 1975 to 1979.

The engagement news of the pop star Cher comes as a surprise to the fans. Edwards was in a relationship with model and T.V. star Amber Rose. He has a three-year-old son Slash Electric Alexander Edwards, with Amber Rose. Edwards was accused of cheating multiple times by Amber Rose during their relationship.

Fans have shared their thoughts on the news on Twitter.

One Twitter user wrote that he is suspicious of his (Edwards) intentions towards Cher. Cher has also fought back against such tweets. She writes that she was not born yesterday, and she knows that there are no guarantees, and anytime you make a choice, you take a chance, and she has always taken chances.

FAQs:

What is the actual name of Cher?

Her real name is Cherilyn Sarkisian.

Where was Cher born?

Cher was born in El Centro, California, USA.
